They help filter URLs likely vulnerable to specific attacks

go install github.com/tomnomnom/gf@latest
export PATH=$PATH:~/go/bin
git clone https://github.com/1ndianl33t/Gf-Patterns
mkdir ~/.gf
cp Gf-Patterns/*.json ~/.gf


cat urls.txt | gf xss


                                                                                         
                                                                                           Common GF Patterns

These patterns detect possible vulnerable parameters.

Pattern	Detects
gf xss	XSS parameters
gf sqli	SQL injection
gf ssrf	SSRF
gf lfi	Local file inclusion
gf redirect	Open redirect
gf rce	Command injection
gf idor	IDOR indicators
gf debug_logic	Debug endpoints
